Large Movie Review Dataset v1.0

Overview

This dataset contains movie reviews along with their associated binary
sentiment polarity labels. It is intended to serve as a benchmark for
sentiment classification. This document outlines how the dataset was
gathered, and how to use the files provided. 

Dataset 

The dataset contains 50,000 reviews split evenly into 25k train, 1250 for validation,
and the rest 1250 for test. The overall distribution of labels is balanced (25k
pos and 25k neg). 

Files

1. train.csv, used to train you model
2. val.csv, used to validate your model and select the "winning" model
3. test.csv, this file does not have label. You need use it as input (features), and make your predictions. 